Package model.json

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Data
    Bean to store generic data generated by a sensor.
    DataNode
    Node storing data collected from a sensor to adapt it to the JSON parser.
    Motes
    Bean for the storage of information about the motes.
    Sender
    Bean containing the information about a data sender (motes acting as sender).
    Sink
    Bean containing the information about a sink (motes acting as sink).
